Your guide to seeing the L.A. Rams at the Coliseum

By Lorena Iñiguez Elebee
Sep. 12, 2016
9:46 AM
  • Facebook
  • Twitter
  • Show more sharing options
Share
  • Facebook
  • Twitter
  • LinkedIn
  • Email

After 20 years, Los Angeles Rams fans are able to see their team play in the L.A. Memorial Coliseum. Going to the game comes with its own questions though: Where to sit? Where should you park? And most importantly, when and where can you tailgate?
